{"id":305320,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-成都访民连续三天省政府上访，多人被殴/","date":"2013-07-24T12:18:43Z","modified":"2013-07-24T12:18:43Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民连续三天省政府上访，多人被殴打（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员徐闯报道）听说中央调查组进驻成都，</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日，青羊区访民邓晓英，帅正秀，叶俊华，，廖才俐，何艾琴，黄丽，新都访民叶尚洪，刘堂富，青白江访民林德群、王玉英等几百访民在省政府上访。</span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据青羊区访民邓晓英说：当时把青羊区的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>个人叫进去接谈，出来后听说，外面警察就开始抓人，打人，强行把其余访民带走，带到三环外的金牛区分流中心，叫各自当地政府接走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日，成都青羊区残疾访民廖才俐（残疾人）听说今天是局长接待日，到青羊区政府门口上访，其有智力残疾的女儿李丹，也到青羊区政府门口找妈妈，结果被警察殴打至昏迷，群众打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，但无人理睬。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据围观群众说：打伤人后，警察都把自己的警号撕掉，继续暴力驱散访民。多名路人拍照被抢走手机删除内容后才归还，路人气氛的说：“这就是和谐社会？”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据伤者母亲廖才俐说：过了半个多小时，才有人将李丹扶起送往草市街派出所，但既没有做笔录也没有受理他们的案件，很多访民帮助打青羊区督查和成都市局督查，但督查均不作为，没有到现场了解情况也没有处置打人的警官。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>廖才俐向本网信息员介绍：她家住在草市街正街上，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">08</span><span>年被强拆后，至今没有得到妥善处理，因此他们逐级反映到北京，但不仅不能解决问题，还经常被殴打和关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日，来自四川各地的访民约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>人，再次到省政府门口聚集，要求见中央巡视组的官员，被强行绑架上大巴，送往金牛分流中心等待各自的政府截访人员接回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>一位被绑架到金牛分流中心的访民向本网信息员说：他见到地下躺着一个访民，没有人理睬，不知道是哪里的，估计又是被打伤，她指控说，现在警察出来都不带警号，谁打了你根本没办法说清楚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oGyxlIQlT80/Ue-virY2F5I/AAAAAAAAlxk/hWg7sxLm40Y/s1600/IMG_20130723_171057.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oGyxlIQlT80/Ue-virY2F5I/AAAAAAAAlxk/hWg7sxLm40Y/s320/IMG_20130723_171057.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GYBY_5eCytU/Ue-vtoGK6EI/AAAAAAAAlyE/MfmLyLLlXLg/s1600/IMG_20130723_175415.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GYBY_5eCytU/Ue-vtoGK6EI/AAAAAAAAlyE/MfmLyLLlXLg/s320/IMG_20130723_175415.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pjc5tDOdg2g/Ue-vjnGTrxI/AAAAAAAAlxs/71zDfYQzMEM/s1600/IMG_20130723_175424.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-pjc5tDOdg2g/Ue-vjnGTrxI/AAAAAAAAlxs/71zDfYQzMEM/s320/IMG_20130723_175424.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-1gmYg4ZRlME/Ue-vkx7oWaI/AAAAAAAAlx0/ovn3Bq70AFc/s1600/IMG_20130723_175435.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-1gmYg4ZRlME/Ue-vkx7oWaI/AAAAAAAAlx0/ovn3Bq70AFc/s320/IMG_20130723_175435.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MDEd4RwIC64/Ue-voQahrLI/AAAAAAAAlx8/H-N48fGgv0Y/s1600/IMG_20130723_175445.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MDEd4RwIC64/Ue-voQahrLI/AAAAAAAAlx8/H-N48fGgv0Y/s320/IMG_20130723_175445.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9Tg9_p1sD8Q/Ue-wJzZbAtI/AAAAAAAAlyg/nvIv5yVc6FY/s1600/%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E5%25A4%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2584%25B8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9Tg9_p1sD8Q/Ue-wJzZbAtI/AAAAAAAAlyg/nvIv5yVc6FY/s320/%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E5%25A4%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2584%25B8%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vEufswrABrk/Ue-wNWVfDXI/AAAAAAAAlyw/33rzOGF_XMc/s1600/%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-vEufswrABrk/Ue-wNWVfDXI/AAAAAAAAlyw/33rzOGF_XMc/s320/%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z1s1fdH9r4Q/Ue-wJ64sCJI/AAAAAAAAlyc/YVxp-MNbCDQ/s1600/%25E8%2584%259A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-z1s1fdH9r4Q/Ue-wJ64sCJI/AAAAAAAAlyc/YVxp-MNbCDQ/s320/%25E8%2584%259A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BC%25A4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IwBiEy_cKKk/Ue-wTgnkdgI/AAAAAAAAly4/zU0rH8SPW9U/s1600/24%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BC%25A4%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IwBiEy_cKKk/Ue-wTgnkdgI/AAAAAAAAly4/zU0rH8SPW9U/s320/24%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BC%25A4%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AE%25BF%25E6%25B0%2591.